snippet.title: Picket Line Official Trailer | September 2023
snippet.description:
This casual tower defense game tells a story of factory strikes and workers' rights in 20th century industrial Zagreb. 
Find it, wishlist it and review it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2409140/Picket_Line/?beta=0
Find us also on Discord! https://discord.com/invite/QdHxVCzuv5
